items.text: Test Reports -- This dashboard test attempt details for users in your scope. You can use the filters to focus on one user, course, or test. You can also choose a date range for results with the Test Attempt Date filter. The report defaults to test attempts from the last 31 days. Adjusting the Test Attempt Date range may affect data load times.
